title: Merry Christmas, Drake & Josh[2008]DvDRip[Eng][Xvid]
description: Merry Christmas, Drake & Josh is a television movie, and the first new program that came out of the Drake & Josh franchise in over a year.Drake Bell, Josh Peck, Miranda Cosgrove, Nancy Sullivan and Jonathan Goldstein reprise their roles as Drake Parker, Josh Nichols, Megan Parker, Audrey Parker, and Walter Nichols respectively; several recurring characters from the TV series also reappeared. The film aired on December 5, 2008 as a Nickelodeon Original Movie.The movie is similar to "Go Hollywood", returning it to its film roots.
